channel.title: Cool, I mean Hello
channel.description:
Wow so really I deleted every thing that had to do with rs cheating when I gave up on rs. Recently I got back to playing, I went looking for kaitnieks to see that it was gone, of course I did not bother to look any further.
Well after a complete 24 hours of no sleep playing a silly game I got to remembering what wonderful times my pc had playing rs with out me there :D
Thanks to scar I can mine rune loved that program loved those scrips. Sadly enough I'm a leach, I could never get my brain around Perl, think I just lacked the devotion to write a script of my own.
Happy to see that scar is still around and kicking. :cool: I might have to give it a second try.
Really like to get my mage up to 94 with that new enchant onyx spell. ;)
